Source.Contents:
/#
 Defines the method for calculating the gain in the period where the Target Knock-Out event occurs (Exact, Exclusive, Inclusive).
 #/
enum FpML5.recordkeeping.FxTargetStyleEnum {
    # The gain for the knockout period is adjusted to yield a final accumulated value equal to the target level.
    Exact 
    # The gain for the knockout period is adjusted to zero i.e. the target yields zero value in the final period.
    Exclusive 
    # The gain for the knockout period is equal to the whole benefit of the final fixing over spot i.e. the final accumulated value may exceed the target level.
    Inclusive 

}

Exact.Doc: The gain for the knockout period is adjusted to yield a final accumulated value equal to the target level.
Exact.Name: Exact

Exclusive.Doc: The gain for the knockout period is adjusted to zero i.e. the target yields zero value in the final period.
Exclusive.Name: Exclusive

Inclusive.Doc: The gain for the knockout period is equal to the whole benefit of the final fixing over spot i.e. the final accumulated value may exceed the target level.
Inclusive.Name: Inclusive
